OL,3,C'How hard is it to bake a potato?' -
OL,4,CHeadteacher criticises food at his
OL,5,Cschool
OL,7,FA headteacher has apologised for the
OL,8,F"completely unacceptable" food
OL,9,Fprovided at his own school in a letter
OL,10,Fsent to parents.
OL,12,FJason Ashley, head of Redbridge
OL,13,FCommunity School in Southampton,
OL,14,Fasked: "How difficult is it to bake a
OL,15,Fpotato?"
OL,17,FThe secondary school's dinners are
OL,18,Fprovided by Chartwells, a national
OL,19,Fcatering company.
