OL,3,C'How hard is it to bake a potato?' -
OL,4,CHeadteacher criticises food at his
OL,5,Cschool
OL,7,FHe added: "We have concluded with our
OL,8,Fphoto evidence that Chartwells do seem
OL,9,Fto be unable to 'bake a potato'
OL,10,Fcorrectly.
OL,12,F"Our evidence shows that in recent
OL,13,Ftimes portions have gotten smaller,
OL,14,Fwhilst prices have risen.
OL,16,F"For example, recently it was British
OL,17,F'pie week' and the pie served was of
OL,18,Fextremely poor quality when compared
OL,19,Fto our partner schools."
