OL,3,C'How hard is it to bake a potato?' -
OL,4,CHeadteacher criticises food at his
OL,5,Cschool
OL,7,FMr Ashley said he could "no longer
OL,8,Ftolerate, provide reasons or even
OL,9,Fjustify to you the unacceptable nature
OL,10,Fof the food".
OL,12,FHe added: "I hope that you are as
OL,13,Fangry and as disappointed as me. For
OL,14,Fthose of you that pay from your hard
OL,15,Fearned wages ` I can only apologise
OL,16,Fand I am sorry."
