OL,3,C'How hard is it to bake a potato?' -
OL,4,CHeadteacher criticises food at his
OL,5,Cschool
OL,7,FIt is understood that there were some
OL,8,Foperational challenges at the school
OL,9,Fwhich Chartwells had been seeking to
OL,10,Faddress, including staffing challenges
OL,11,Fwhich had temporarily affected service
OL,12,Flevels.
OL,14,FIt is also understood there has been
OL,15,Fno reduction in portion sizes or an
OL,16,Fincrease in the price of meals at the
OL,17,Fschool in the last two years.
