OL,3,C'How hard is it to bake a potato?' -
OL,4,CHeadteacher criticises food at his
OL,5,Cschool
OL,7,FIn a statement, a spokesman for
OL,8,FChartwells apologised and said: "We
OL,9,Frecognise the importance of school
OL,10,Fmeals, and our teams work hard to
OL,11,Fprovide good quality food every day.
OL,13,F"We apologise that in this instance
OL,14,Four usual level of service has fallen
OL,15,Fbelow the high standards we demand.
OL,17,F"We are committed to working in
OL,18,Fcollaboration with the school and are
OL,19,Fimplementing an immediate action plan
OL,20,Fto rectify these issues."
