OL,3,C'How hard is it to bake a potato?' -
OL,4,CHeadteacher criticises food at his
OL,5,Cschool
OL,7,FThe organisation previously faced a
OL,8,Fbacklash in 2021 after photographs of
OL,9,Ftheir free school meal parcels were
OL,10,Fshared and criticised on social media.
OL,12,FFormer prime minister Boris Johnson
OL,13,Fsaid in a Commons address the parcels
OL,14,Fwere an "insult" to the families who
OL,15,Freceived them, while former home
OL,16,Fsecretary Priti Patel said they were
OL,17,F"appalling in every way".
